1)  ANALYSIS OF THE TARGET IMAGE

●  Total Blocks and Layers  
   – There are 9 total blocks in the scene.  
   – Left “tower” structure uses 6 blocks stacked in 5 layers:  
     1st layer (bottom): two red U‐shaped pieces side by side  
     2nd layer: one blue cube  
     3rd layer: one green rectangular block  
     4th layer: one red arch block  
     5th layer: one orange triangular “roof”  
   – Right “cart” structure uses 3 blocks in 2 layers:  
     1st layer (bottom): two horizontal red cylinders (the “wheels”)  
     2nd layer (top): one yellow rectangular block  

●  Spatial Relationships  
   – Left tower (bottom to top):  
     •  The two red U‐shapes (open side up) support a single blue cube centered above them.  
     •  A green rectangular block spans across the top of the blue cube.  
     •  A red arch block sits directly atop that green layer.  
     •  An orange roof‐shaped block finishes the tower at the top.  
   – Right cart (bottom to top):  
     •  Two red cylinders lie horizontally next to each other.  
     •  A yellow rectangular block rests on top, bridging both cylinders.  

2)  SELECTING THE DICTIONARY BLOCKS

Based on color, shape, and the unrotated orientations in the dictionary, the required blocks (by index) are:

●  Left Tower:  
   – 2 × index 2  (red U‐shaped block)  
   – 1 × index 5  (blue cube)  
   – 1 × index 7  (green rectangular block)  
   – 1 × index 1  (red arch block)  
   – 1 × index 15 (orange triangular “roof”)  

●  Right Cart:  
   – 2 × index 12 (red cylinder, horizontal orientation)  
   – 1 × index 9  (yellow rectangular block, horizontal orientation)  

3)  ASSEMBLY ORDER

Use the following step‐by‐step sequence (in JSON‐style format):

{
  Step1:  "Move block with index 2",
  Step2:  "Move block with index 2",
  Step3:  "Move block with index 5",
  Step4:  "Move block with index 7",
  Step5:  "Move block with index 1",
  Step6:  "Move block with index 15",
  Step7:  "Move block with index 12",
  Step8:  "Move block with index 12",
  Step9:  "Move block with index 9"
}
